Class UserFieldGenerator

  • java.lang.Object
    • teal.core.AbstractElement
      • teal.sim.SimObj
        • teal.physics.UserFieldGenerator
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.beans.PropertyChangeListener, java.io.Serializable, java.util.EventListener, javax.swing.event.DocumentListener, HasID, TElement, THasPropertyChange, GenericFieldGenerator, TSimElement

    public class UserFieldGenerator
extends SimObj
implements GenericFieldGenerator, javax.swing.event.DocumentListener
    UserFieldGenerator implements GenericFieldGenerator to produce a field based on a user-supplied function, parsed from JFormattedTextField. Currently only used in the MappingFields simulation.
    Version:
    $Revision: 1.6 $
    Author:
    mesrob, Andrew McKinney, Phil Bailey, Michael Danziger
